{"tid":778632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門氣象局稱下午視情況考慮是否改掛8號風球（14/8）","createTime":"2018-08-14T00:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T01:25:16.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"117be410e1cc05df7091010418997d1f1716f0b6","tid":778632,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:14:16.000Z","msg":"(澳門電台消息) 本澳仍然懸掛 3號風球。氣象局稱，下午會視乎情況考慮是否改掛 8號風球。<br />\n<br />\n氣象局稱，於早上7時，熱帶風暴&ldquo;貝碧嘉&rdquo;正集結於本澳以南約 150公里，以緩慢速度向北移動，正逐漸接近本澳，受其環流影響，本澳今明兩日有大驟雨及雷暴，今日稍後風力有所增加。(鄭家賜 羅曉彬)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tdm.com.mo/c_news/radio_news.php?id=387169#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftdm.com.mo%2Fc_news%2Fradio_news.php%3Fid%3D387169%23&d=WU70cn3kxO7zAgzGaBbBPTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=afa88e5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tdm.com.mo/c_news/radio_news.php?id=387169#</a>"},{"pid":"ca86f5c022c97ba77405384d0a2d07de3013cadc","tid":778632,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:34:50.000Z","msg":"水為財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0d81f8285465302cf61d4a1f9b83f41dff7ca5a","tid":778632,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:36:05.000Z","msg":"天佑澳豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addd67306bc08d6d898d988ce73ad673225ac2a6","tid":778632,"uid":188112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc26f15ac9b4dcf47233f73c4831c459b8c8612","tid":778632,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"香港市民稱下午視情況考慮是否提早收工返屋企開檯"},{"pid":"309baed883b3b64bcb9f07ecf4d43c2ebd7ea557","tid":778632,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:06:22.000Z","msg"